                            <p>Ola comes up with various ride offers from time-to-time. To avail these offers, you need to apply a coupon while booking your Ola ride.</p>
                            <p>To <strong>apply a coupon</strong> on your Ola ride, all you need to do is- <br>- Select a cab category and tap <strong>RIDE NOW</strong> or <strong>RIDE LATER</strong> (if available ) to make a booking. <br>- Tap <strong>Coupons Available</strong> option and select the coupon you want to use.<br><strong>Note</strong> - The number of Ola coupons you have is displayed on clicking <strong>Coupons Available</strong> option. If you don't see a coupon code but know the code, you can always enter it here.</p>
