                            <p>At the end of the trip, you can always check the discount applied on your total fare in the invoice sent to you on your registered email ID.</p>
                            <p>If a coupon code for availing a particular offer on your Ola ride could not be applied, it may be due to the following reasons but not limited to these only: -<br> <br>- Offer validity has expired <br>- Offer is not valid in your city.<br>- Offer is applicable to a particular ride category.<br>- Offer is valid only on specific days and during certain hours of a day.<br>- Offer is valid on a particular number of rides.<br> <br>Every time we come up with an offer for you, offer details are sent to your email ID registered with Ola. We request you to check the terms and conditions applicable to the offer as terms and conditions for each offer can be unique and different from the previous offers.</p>
